  "subject": "x86: add handle_irq() to allow interrupt injection",
  "body": "Xen uses a different interrupt path, so introduce handle_irq() to\nallow interrupts to be inserted into the normal interrupt path.  This\nis handled slightly differently on 32 and 64-bit.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeremy Fitzhardinge <jeremy.fitzhardinge@citrix.com>\nSigned-off-by: Ingo Molnar <mingo@elte.hu>",
